===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# An act or instance of [[deflate|deflating]].
#: ''The loss caused utter '''deflation''' and disappointment among the fans.''
#: {{ant|en|inflation}}
# {{lb|en|economics}} A [[decrease]] in the general price level, that is, in the [[nominal]] [[cost]] of [[goods]] and [[services]] as well as [[wages]].
#: {{syn|en|disinflation}}
#: {{ant|en|inflation}}
# {{lb|en|economics|euphemistic}} An economic [[contraction]].
